@node Note "AmiGameBoy Emulator."

    Note from Author:
    -----------------

    After some time (One Year!!!) I back with a new version of this
emulator.

    I decided one year ago make AmiGameBoy Shareware, but i am very very
busy with my job and AmiMasterGear to continue with it.

    To this reason i decided spread a new freeware version of AmiGameBoy.

